rop the +6 int without up-ing something else.<br><br>Thanks again.<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ucabottp.showPublicProfile?language=EN>CabotTP</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/11/01 8:53:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=284.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Robe upgrade</span><hr size=1> <br>My advice if you mainly solo is start looking for +mana.  To do this, you need to get over the 200 int mark, and then keep pushing for better +int items.  The larger +int amounts you can get in fewer items leaves more &quot;empty&quot; slots to put +mana items into.  I'm 53 atm, and since around level 46 or 47 I've been wearing Shardtooth's Flayed Skin just because I haven't gotten a chance at anything with more +mana.  It's +35 hp/mana and some decent AC (14?).<br><br> <p><BR>Cabot Coriolis of Tholuxe Paells<BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uarantrunemaster.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Arant Runemaster</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(6/13/01 10:53:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=284.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Robe upgrade</span><hr size=1> Hunt in Skyshrine and get a guardian robe around lvl 40+. ac12 int8 sta5 mana45 fire8 cold8 - about equal to a Froglock bonecaster robe, except- ITS 11k cheaper! hehe, aka FREE. Get one, they're great. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td